data.description: This beautiful custom built 3-bedroom 2.5 bathroom home is waiting for a new buyer! This stunner has a great open layout with windows galore! Located minutes from Downtown, and near the Heights area! This bright and sunshiny home is perfect for entertaining with a fabulous kitchen and boasting granite counter tops, newer stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry. With incredible skyline views of Downtown, Medical Center, and Galleria!!    Agents, bring your clients to view this amazing home. Schedule your showings today!!
